THE CREEK NATION, PETITIONER, v. THE UNITED STATES THE SEMINOLE NATION, PETITIONER, v. THE UNITED STATES [No. F-369] [No. L-88]

[Ante, pages 591, 723 ; 318 U. S. —]

*736Mr. Justice Black

delivered the opinion of the court.'
